 large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理(你)傾</span></span></strong>，了解街坊了解市民，<em>make connection</em>，懇請大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">落區</span></span></strong>做野，建設自己家園，幫下黃色嘅同路人！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">潛滋暗長！忍耐負重！<br />\nBe Water! Be Smart!</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">注意事項</span></span>⚠️：<br />\n1. 政府想透過示威者=破壞，政府=復修，改善形象，不要中計，多文宣<br />\n2. 施政報告會派糖，想轉移視線，對準不公義嘅制度，堅持普選立法會、普選行政長官<br />\n3. 警方會扮好人，發現紙包唔住火，開始關心你啦，唔好比佢地呃到人，不信任<br />\n4. 獨立調查？記住死左嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">連登五毛滲透嚴重，大家要帶腦睇post<br />\n最新技倆：煽動最激進/冇底線暴力行為<br />\n指責停勇武=唔做嘢、完啦、失敗啦<br />\n然後推大量呢類post上熱門打擊信心<br />\n另外，五毛已經識得整文宣，文宣互毆<br />\n總之頭腦要清醒，好易中伏（中過伏</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n政府損失：0人，民望、信譽跌至谷底<br />\n香港人損失：2363人+多人曾經活著<br />\n<br />\n抗爭轉型及進化建議：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持久戰拖垮邪惡</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">重要目標：</span></strong>11月24號區議會選舉<br />\n香港民主及人權法案<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">防範：</span></strong>掌心雷、利誘淺黃淺藍市民、抹黑<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">流水式示威：</span></strong>警察舉旗咪去另一個地方示威，香港咁多地方可以去，佢想捉你，你咪話走緊囉，太多人行得慢好正常，合情合理合法！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">適當武力/自衛反擊：</span></strong>合情又合理！<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>游擊戰？：</strong></span>對抗黑社會/恐怖分子（文宣解釋）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">創意活動：抗爭融入生活</span></strong>唱歌比賽？跑步大叫？商場罷買？摺紙？18區和你傾、流水式返學返工#Shout4HK#諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：保持民意、減少被捕<br />\n建議：落街和你傾，落區啦！文宣！<br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化黃色陣營、黃色經濟圈<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、啓蒙思想、人滅心不滅<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭</span><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMdiioB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMdiioB.jpg&h=7e10cb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨、新華社、環球時報、人民日報<br />\n2.誤導：警總救護車、雷射槍、9吋尖刀等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者/黑警：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n11.警察濫權、濫捕、暴力執法、恐嚇<br />\n12.利用親中人士發表「假」權威言論<br />\n13.用盡手段打壓反對聲音<br />\n14.矮化示威者為甲由、yellow object<br />\n15.假對話，真緊急法：獨裁特首<br />\n16.高壓統治，嚇到你噤聲<br />\n諗到再加</span><br />\nSir, my concern is not whether God is on our side; my greatest concern is to be on God's side, for God is always right."},{"pid":"4ea4f012585bff8ccd7238605668d816220da0f7","tid":1647920,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"612 721 805 831 921 101"},{"pid":"cd03bf8b97b6e140d269076b40cee34de816d8e2","tid":1647920,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:24:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0UOaVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0UOaVn.png&h=c7fd48b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAhQxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAhQxD.png&h=d230a326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!<br />\n<br />\n更多作品：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%2523XinniethePooh%26src%3Dtypeahead_click&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=e25ad15b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click</a>"},{"pid":"67f6760a2175ed4911055974f67fa21d910a2040","tid":1647920,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kE0NvXZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkE0NvXZ.png&h=2d48d7e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d4f5e92ac0d5ffd48d55854688751644f19588c","tid":